@startuml Current Architecture - Class Diagram

title Current Inventory Kamera Architecture (v1.3.17)
note as N1
  **Problems:**
  - Tight coupling to WinForms
  - System.Drawing (Windows-only)
  - Hard-coded coordinates
  - No abstraction for testing
end note

package "WinForms UI" {
  class MainForm {
    - inventoryKamera : InventoryKamera
    + StartScan() : void
    + UpdateProgress(int, int) : void
    + ShowErrors(string) : void
  }

  class UserInterface <<static>> {
    + SetGearPictureBox(Bitmap) : void
    + IncrementArtifactCount() : void
    + AddError(string) : void
    {note: Thread-safe UI updates from workers}
  }
}

package "Data & Models" {
  class InventoryKamera {
    + Characters : List<Character>
    + Inventory : Inventory
    - workerQueue : Queue<OCRImageCollection>
    - ImageProcessors : List<Thread>
    + GatherData() : void
    - ImageProcessorWorker() : void
    {note: Orchestrates multi-threaded scanning}
  }

  class Inventory {
    + Weapons : List<Weapon>
    + Artifacts : List<Artifact>
    + Materials : List<Material>
    + Size : int
  }

  class Character {
    + Name : string
    + Level : int
    + Constellation : int
    + Weapon : Weapon
    + Artifacts : Artifact[]
  }

  class Weapon {
    + Name : string
    + Level : int
    + Refinement : int
    + Rarity : int
    + EquippedCharacter : string
  }

  class Artifact {
    + SetName : string
    + Slot : string
    + Level : int
    + Rarity : int
    + MainStat : Stat
    + SubStats : List<Stat>
    + EquippedCharacter : string
    + Locked : bool
  }

  class GOOD {
    + Export(InventoryKamera) : string
    {note: Generates GOOD JSON format}
  }
}

package "Scanning" {
  abstract class Scraper {
    # {static} engines : ConcurrentBag<TesseractEngine>
    # {static} GenshinProcesor : GenshinProcesor
    + {static} InitializeScrapers() : void
    # GetEngine() : TesseractEngine
    # ReturnEngine(TesseractEngine) : void
    {note: Manages pool of 8 Tesseract engines}
  }

  class ArtifactScraper {
    + ScanArtifacts() : void
    + QueueScan(int) : void
    + CatalogueFromBitmapsAsync(List<Bitmap>, int) : Task<Artifact>
    - IsSanctified(Bitmap) : bool
    - GetSubstatsBitmap(Bitmap) : Bitmap
    {note: Hard-coded coordinates for 16:9 and 16:10}
  }

  class WeaponScraper {
    + ScanWeapons() : void
    + CatalogueFromBitmapsAsync(List<Bitmap>, int) : Task<Weapon>
  }

  class CharacterScraper <<static>> {
    + ScanCharacters(ref List<Character>) : void
    + ScanMainCharacterName() : string
  }

  class MaterialScraper {
    + Scan_Materials(ref Inventory) : void
  }

  class OCRImageCollection {
    + Bitmaps : List<Bitmap>
    + Type : string
    + Id : int
    {note: Wrapper for queueing to worker threads}
  }
}

package "Game Integration" {
  class Navigation <<static>> {
    + {static} GetItemCard() : Bitmap
    + {static} CaptureWindow() : Bitmap
    + {static} SystemClick(int, int) : void
    + {static} SendKey(Keys) : void
    + {static} IsNormal : bool
    {note: Windows-specific: Graphics.CopyFromScreen}
  }

  class GenshinProcesor <<static>> {
    + {static} CompareColors(Color, Color) : bool
    + {static} CopyBitmap(Bitmap, Rectangle) : Bitmap
    + {static} Mappings : Dictionary<ulong, string>
    + {static} UpdateCharacterName(string, string) : void
    {note: Image processing using System.Drawing}
  }
}

package "Data Management" {
  class DatabaseManager <<static>> {
    + {static} UpdateAll() : void
    - {static} UpdateCharacters() : void
    - {static} UpdateArtifacts() : void
    - {static} UpdateWeapons() : void
    - {static} UpdateMaterials() : void
    {note: Fetches from GitHub, parses JSON}
  }
}

' Relationships
MainForm --> InventoryKamera : creates/owns
MainForm ..> UserInterface : updates UI

InventoryKamera --> Inventory : manages
InventoryKamera --> Character : collects
InventoryKamera --> OCRImageCollection : enqueues
InventoryKamera ..> ArtifactScraper : calls
InventoryKamera ..> WeaponScraper : calls
InventoryKamera ..> CharacterScraper : calls
InventoryKamera ..> MaterialScraper : calls

Inventory *-- Weapon : contains
Inventory *-- Artifact : contains
Character --> Weapon : equipped
Character --> Artifact : equipped

ArtifactScraper --|> Scraper
WeaponScraper --|> Scraper
MaterialScraper --|> Scraper

Scraper ..> Navigation : uses
Scraper ..> GenshinProcesor : uses
Scraper --> OCRImageCollection : creates

ArtifactScraper ..> UserInterface : updates UI
WeaponScraper ..> UserInterface : updates UI

DatabaseManager ..> GenshinProcesor : loads Mappings

GOOD ..> InventoryKamera : reads data

note bottom of Navigation
  **Windows-Only Dependencies:**
  - Graphics.CopyFromScreen()
  - WindowsInput library
  - System.Drawing.Bitmap
end note

note bottom of Scraper
  **Threading Issues:**
  - Tesseract 5.2.0 deadlocks
  - 8 engine pool, 2-3 workers
  - 30-second timeout workaround
end note

note bottom of ArtifactScraper
  **Hard-coded Coordinates:**
  Lines 250-350 have magic numbers
  for 16:9 (0.4216) and 16:10 (0.3682)
  Sanctified shift: 0.0520 / 0.0471
end note

@enduml
